  <brief_title>PDR001 Plus LAG525 for Patients With Advanced Solid and Hematologic Malignancies</brief_title>
  <official_title>Modular Phase 2 Study to Link Combination Immune-therapy to Patients With Advanced Solid and Hematologic Malignancies. Module 9: PDR001 Plus LAG525 for Patients With Advanced Solid and Hematologic Malignancies.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
